data.description: Lovely 4-sided Brick Home in sought after Hampton, Ga. location.  Well Maintained, clean inspection report !!  This floor plan offers PRIVATE BATHROOMS IN ALL BEDROOMS !  Master bath boasts dual vanities, garden tub, with separate shower.  Gourmet Kitchen with granite countertops, SS appliances, Island breakfast bar, separate Dining room, Living room and Great room, with hardwoods floors through home.  This home has plenty of space/storage and it also has a huge backyard with a covered patio for entertaining and side entry garage with plenty of parking if needed !  There is an option for a 5 Bedrm if you want to do the construction & put a door up.  FYI Seller's are leaving SS Frig., Washing & Dryer, and Riding Lawnmower !
